# AI Image Text Editor - Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and add your API keys

# ============================================================
# ALL APIS ARE FREE! Get at least one for AI image editing
# ============================================================

# OPTION 1: HuggingFace API (FREE & RECOMMENDED) - ChatGPT-like image editing
# Uses Instruct-Pix2Pix model which transforms your image based on text
# Get your FREE token at: https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens
HUGGING_FACE_API_KEY=hf_your_token_here

# OPTION 2: Fal.ai API (FREE tier) - High quality ChatGPT-like editing
# Get your FREE key at: https://fal.ai/dashboard/keys
FAL_KEY=your_fal_key_here

# OPTION 3: Replicate API (FREE tier) - Another alternative
# Get your FREE token at: https://replicate.com/account/api-tokens
REPLICATE_API_TOKEN=your_replicate_token_here

# Google Gemini API (FREE) - For AI image description
# Get your FREE key at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# ============================================================
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Get at least HUGGING_FACE_API_KEY (easiest/fastest)
# 3. OR set environment variable directly:
#    Windows PowerShell: $env:HUGGING_FACE_API_KEY="hf_xxx"
#    Mac/Linux: export HUGGING_FACE_API_KEY="hf_xxx"
# ============================================================

# PRIORITY ORDER for AI Image Editing:
# 1. FAL_KEY (best quality, uses FLUX Pro)
# 2. HUGGING_FACE_API_KEY (good quality, uses Instruct-Pix2Pix)
# 3. REPLICATE_API_TOKEN (good quality, uses Instruct-Pix2Pix)
